10.23.23  10:39 pm   Hi! So today in my math class when I was zoning out during a quiz, I realized how stupid I am with my words. Wonderful and creative people like you create these really amazing, deep songs effortlessly while I'm over here struggling to form a decent sentence or drawing.

     How do you do it all? What does it take to create shit that people would care about and remember?

      I try to tell myself that it takes courage to be bad at something, knowing that if you put time and energy into it'll all work out in the end. I'm just in a really dark place right now and would love to hear back from you... :)
